NIZATION] firm po ni Atty. [ORGANIZATION] for final assessment. And I'm sorry to advise as of now your account is possible for case filing.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 47.0, "start": 46.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [{"source": "ngram_anchor", "original": "kayo ng proper", "corrected": "kayo ng demand", "confidence_delta": 1.0}], "refined_text": "So, para ma-hold yung possible legal action po ni [BANK NAME], ang kailangan po ni [BANK NAME] sir is magkaroon kayo ng demand arrangement with them.", "original_text": "So, para ma-hold yung possible legal action po ni [BANK NAME], ang kailangan po ni [BANK NAME] sir is magkaroon kayo ng proper arrangement with them.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 48.0, "start": 47.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [], "refined_text": "It's like a win-win situation on both sides. Kayo, magkaroon kayo ng arrangement kay bank which is feasible pagdating sa inyo.", "original_text": "It's like a win-win situation on both sides. Kayo, magkaroon kayo ng arrangement kay bank which is feasible pagdating sa inyo.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 49.0, "start": 48.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "greeting", "corrections": [{"source": "ngram_anchor", "original": "banko magkaroon pa", "corrected": "baka magkaroon pa", "confidence_delta": 1.0}, {"source": "gemini", "original": "nagbabayating", "corrected": "nagbabayad", "confidence_delta": null}], "refined_text": "and also yung baka magkaroon pa yun ng arrangement at makitaan na may nagbabayad kayo sa kanila. Hello? Hello, sir?", "original_text": "and also yung banko magkaroon pa yun ng arrangement at makitaan na may nagbabayating kayo sa kanila. Hello? Hello, sir?", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 50.0, "start": 49.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [], "refined_text": "So, yun po, sir. Hindi kaya, sir, yung required na down payment, which is fifty percent nga. Tanungin kita