 kay banko na magkaroon ng arrangement. Kami, sir, we will process lang po.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 68.0, "start": 67.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [{"source": "gemini", "original": "sinasabihin", "corrected": "sinasabi", "confidence_delta": null}], "refined_text": "And regarding din po, sir, sinasabi niyo ng collection, sir, we're not doing that kind of collection na para lang po mag-collect.", "original_text": "And regarding din po, sir, sinasabihin niyo ng collection, sir, we're not doing that kind of collection na para lang po mag-collect.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 69.0, "start": 68.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [{"source": "ngram_anchor", "original": "itong account ninyo", "corrected": "itong account niyo", "confidence_delta": 1.0}], "refined_text": "We are making a collection to make an arrangement with the bank. So, ganito, gawin natin arrangement itong account niyo. Process natin for [VALUE]six months.", "original_text": "We are making a collection to make an arrangement with the bank. So, ganito, gawin natin arrangement itong account ninyo. Process natin for [VALUE]six months.", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 70.0, "start": 69.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "negotiation", "corrections": [{"source": "gemini", "original": "mag-big kiyang", "corrected": "magbigay", "confidence_delta": null}], "refined_text": "Last time, nare-required kayo mag-settled tama, [VALUE] pesos na down payment. Kung hindi kayo yun, sir, mag-settled kayo, magbigay", "original_text": "Last time, nare-required kayo mag-settled tama, [VALUE] pesos na down payment. Kung hindi kayo yun, sir, mag-settled kayo, mag-big kiyang", "low_confidence_words": []}, {"end": 71.0, "start": 70.0, "speaker": "agent", "anchor_mode": "general", "corrections": [{"source": "ngram_anchor", "original": "itong account ninyo", "corrected": "itong account niyo", "confidence_delta": 1.0}], "refined_text": "k